    "abstract": "We present a candidate sequential function for a VDF protocol to be used within the Ethereum ecosystem. The new function, called  MinRoot, is an optimized iterative algebraic transformation and is a strict improvement over competitors VeeDo and Sloth++. We analyze various attacks on sequentiality and suggest weakened versions for public scrutiny. We also announce bounties on certain research directions in cryptanalysis.",
    "keywords": [
      "VDF"
    ],
